1. Radium floaters;
2. Physician's and surgeons' instrument floaters, which may include coverage of furniture,
fixtures, and a tenant insured's interest in improvements and betterments of buildings located
in that portion of the premises occupied by the insured in the practice of his or her profession;
3. Pattern and die floaters;
